reviewText: Many of the Lassie episodes are available on YouTube, but these two are not. "The Disappearance "  explains how Lassie and Ranger Corey Stuart met, setting the stage for a later transition of ownership from Timmy. "Look Homeward" was on a Viewmaster I remember from my childhood.  I really enjoyed reminders from the past, and was struck even more by how well-trained Lassie was for this show. Reminder: this DVD was released overseas and so you need a region free DVR to be able to watch it.
